  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients scheduled for elective surgery will undergo 4 week course of trimodal&#xD;
      prehabilitation&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients with high surgical risk will participate in 4 week prehabilitation that will consist&#xD;
      of 4 stationary sessions - one per week - comprised of: physiotherapy session, psychological&#xD;
      session and nutritional advice. During first session each patient will receive an activity&#xD;
      monitor and dedicated mobile app that will record his daily performance.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
